WEBVTT

00:04:00.470 --> 00:04:03.530
Like when you grow up and go to school,

00:04:03.530 --> 00:04:07.030
you will sense that you are different.

00:04:07.050 --> 00:04:10.320
Other kids will have mothers
who come to fetch them from school

00:04:10.320 --> 00:04:12.840
but you will only have your father.

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:17.849
Like when WhatsApp groups are formed
to discuss homework,

00:04:17.849 --> 00:04:21.760
all your friends’ mothers will be part of it,
and I will be the only dad out there.

00:04:22.470 --> 00:04:25.740
People will question you about it,

00:04:25.740 --> 00:04:28.550
don’t let those questions bother you.

00:04:29.180 --> 00:04:32.240
Keep your head held high
and honestly answer those questions.